{"id":"687429284607085","from":{"id":"100001695345798","name":"Tyn Aki"},"subject":"Tổng hợp các website hữu ích cho học tiếng Nhật","message":"<p>Tổng hợp các website hữu ích cho học tiếng Nhật.Dấu sao ★ là ad tự đặt theo chủ quan, cao nhất là 5 sao.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>1. Thi ti</strong><strong>ếng Nh</strong><strong>ật JLPT (</strong><strong>日本語能力試験)</strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>1.1 日本語能力試験公式ウェッブサイト (Website chính thức về JLPT)</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jlpt.jp%2F&amp;h=7AQHC_y9P&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/www.jlpt.jp\\/&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fwww.jlpt.jp\\u00252F&amp;h=7AQHC_y9P&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://www.jlpt.jp/</a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>1.2 日本国際教育支援協会 (Website của Hiệp hội Giáo dục Quốc tế Nhật Bản)</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Finfo.jees-jlpt.jp%2F&amp;h=FAQEo-F6q&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/info.jees-jlpt.jp\\/&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Finfo.jees-jlpt.jp\\u00252F&amp;h=FAQEo-F6q&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://info.jees-jlpt.jp</a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>2. Luy</strong><strong>ện thi JLPT</strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>2.1 問題例 | 日本語能力試験 JLPT ★★★★★</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jlpt.jp%2Fsamples%2Fforlearners.html&amp;h=VAQGu9o8K&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/www.jlpt.jp\\/samples\\/forlearners.html&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fwww.jlpt.jp\\u00252Fsamples\\u00252Fforlearners.html&amp;h=VAQGu9o8K&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://www.jlpt.jp/samples/forlearners.html</a></p>\n<p>Mẫu thi thử của chính tổ chức JLPT cung cấp</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>2.2 日本語能力試験学習サイト ★★★★</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjlpt.u-biq.org%2F&amp;h=DAQGmc0G-&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/jlpt.u-biq.org\\/&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fjlpt.u-biq.org\\u00252F&amp;h=DAQGmc0G-&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://jlpt.u-biq.org/</a></p>\n<p>Luyện thi JLPT 4級～1級: ngữ pháp 文法, từ vựng 語彙, chữ Hán 漢字</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>2.3 日本語能力試験web問題-A.C.C.国際交流学園 ★★★★</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.accjapan.com%2Fwebtest%2F&amp;h=BAQHImefl&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/www.accjapan.com\\/webtest\\/&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fwww.accjapan.com\\u00252Fwebtest\\u00252F&amp;h=BAQHImefl&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://www.accjapan.com/webtest/</a></p>\n<p>Luyện thi JLPT N5~N1: ngữ pháp 文法</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>2.4 Lagudi</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Flagudi.net%2F&amp;h=pAQEFokU9&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/lagudi.net\\/&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Flagudi.net\\u00252F&amp;h=pAQEFokU9&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://lagudi.net/</a> ★★★★</p>\n<p>Phân loại ngữ pháp và chữ Hán theo các trình độ thi JLPT.</p>\n<p>Có tiếng Việt.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>2.5 <a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.n-lab.org%2Flibrary%2Fmondai%2Findex.html&amp;h=NAQFrh_zO&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/www.n-lab.org\\/library\\/mondai\\/index.html&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fwww.n-lab.org\\u00252Flibrary\\u00252Fmondai\\u00252Findex.html&amp;h=NAQFrh_zO&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://www.n-lab.org/library/mondai/index.html</a> ★★★</p>\n<p>Phân loại ngữ pháp theo các trình độ thi JLPT</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>2.6 JLPT Level N1,N2, N3, N4, N5 Resources</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tanos.co.uk%2Fjlpt%2F&amp;h=lAQE6WumJ&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/www.tanos.co.uk\\/jlpt\\/&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fwww.tanos.co.uk\\u00252Fjlpt\\u00252F&amp;h=lAQE6WumJ&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://www.tanos.co.uk/jlpt/</a> ★★★★★</p>\n<p>Website cá nhân, các nguồn không đồng bộ.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>2.7 篠崎N1文法対策</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsenzaide.gozaru.jp%2Fbi-index.html&amp;h=_AQFm-aVQ&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/senzaide.gozaru.jp\\/bi-index.html&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fsenzaide.gozaru.jp\\u00252Fbi-index.html&amp;h=_AQFm-aVQ&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://senzaide.gozaru.jp/bi-index.html</a> ★★★★★</p>\n<p>Luyện ngữ pháp N1</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>2.8 Free Japanese study materials</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mlcjapanese.co.jp%2FDownload.htm&amp;h=fAQGvFpoI&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/www.mlcjapanese.co.jp\\/Download.htm&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fwww.mlcjapanese.co.jp\\u00252FDownload.htm&amp;h=fAQGvFpoI&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://www.mlcjapanese.co.jp/Download.htm</a> ★★★★★</p>\n<p>Luyện thi ngữ pháp, từ vựng, Kanji N2, N1 của trường 日本語学校MLC目黒ランゲージセンター</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>2.9 日本語の森　無料日本語レッスン</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nihongonomori.com%2F&amp;h=kAQEWMYx-&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/www.nihongonomori.com\\/&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fwww.nihongonomori.com\\u00252F&amp;h=kAQEWMYx-&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://www.nihongonomori.com/</a> ★★★★★</p>\n<p>Website do giáo viên người Nhật dạy tiếng Nhật miễn phí, chủ yếu bằng video rất hay.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>2.10 JLPT past papers</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tanos.co.uk%2Fjlpt%2Fskills%2Fpastpapers%2F&amp;h=GAQGq5gLF&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/www.tanos.co.uk\\/jlpt\\/skills\\/pastpapers\\/&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fwww.tanos.co.uk\\u00252Fjlpt\\u00252Fskills\\u00252Fpastpapers\\u00252F&amp;h=GAQGq5gLF&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://www.tanos.co.uk/jlpt/skills/pastpapers/</a> ★★★★★</p>\n<p>Bài thi và đáp an thi cũ. N5-N1.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>2.11 JLPT Level Checker</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tanos.co.uk%2Fjlpt%2Flevelcheck%2F&amp;h=WAQE4ReVj&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/www.tanos.co.uk\\/jlpt\\/levelcheck\\/&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fwww.tanos.co.uk\\u00252Fjlpt\\u00252Flevelcheck\\u00252F&amp;h=WAQE4ReVj&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://www.tanos.co.uk/jlpt/levelcheck/</a> ★★★★★</p>\n<p>Test trình độ tiếng Nhật của mình theo các mức N5-N1 của JLPT</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>3. Danh sách l</strong><strong>ớp h</strong><strong>ọc ti</strong><strong>ếng Nh</strong><strong>ật</strong> volunteer trên toàn nước Nhật</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fu-biq.org%2Fvolunteermap.html&amp;h=CAQEZSmiv&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/u-biq.org\\/volunteermap.html&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fu-biq.org\\u00252Fvolunteermap.html&amp;h=CAQEZSmiv&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://u-biq.org/volunteermap.html</a> ★★★★★</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>4. T</strong><strong>ự h</strong><strong>ọc ti</strong><strong>ếng Nh</strong><strong>ật theo course</strong> từ thấp lên cao(không nhất thiết theo JLPT)</p>\n<p>(phần lớn dạy bằng tiếng Anh và tiếng Nhật đơn giản)</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>4.1 Lớp học tiếng Nhật</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Flophoctiengnhat.com%2F&amp;h=NAQFrh_zO&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/lophoctiengnhat.com\\/&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Flophoctiengnhat.com\\u00252F&amp;h=NAQFrh_zO&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://lophoctiengnhat.com/</a> ★★★★★</p>\n<p>Website của Trường ngoại ngữ Việt Nhật, TpHCM. Dạy bằng tiếng Việt.</p>\n<p>Website tự học tiếng Nhật từ chưa biết gì đến trung cấp.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>4.2 U-biq ゆーびっく</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstudy.u-biq.org%2Fenglish.html&amp;h=-AQH_C182&amp;s=1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" onmouseover=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/study.u-biq.org\\/english.html&quot;);\" onclick=\"LinkshimAsyncLink.swap(this, &quot;http:\\/\\/l.facebook.com\\/l.php?u=http\\u00253A\\u00252F\\u00252Fstudy.u-biq.org\\u00252Fenglish.html&amp;h=-AQH_C182&amp;s=1&quot;);\">http://study.u-b